# pages.txt — the handpicked creators this platform scrapes.
#
#   cp pages.txt.example pages.txt      then replace the samples below.
#
# The real pages.txt is gitignored on purpose: a targeting list is real personal
# data about real creators, and it is the one file in this repo most likely to be
# committed by accident.
#
# Format: one creator per line. Blank lines and lines starting with # are skipped.
# A full profile URL or a bare handle both work.
#
# The handles below are SYNTHETIC placeholders (they are not real accounts) — the
# scraper will find nothing until you swap in creators from your own niche. To grow
# this list automatically instead of by hand, run the AutoSearch discovery agent and
# approve its candidates in the Dashboard; the hub appends approved handles here.

https://www.instagram.com/example.fashion.daily
https://www.instagram.com/example.streetstyle
https://www.instagram.com/example.outfitgrid
